<h3 align="right">Advice Column!</h3>

<p>
<img src="/img/rev-head.gif" alt="" width="37" height="40" align="left" />
Let Reverend and his many incarnations (Minister, BigJamie, and others)
answer those questions that get stuck in your craw!</p>

<p><strong style="color: #FF0000;">Warning!</strong><br />
This advice column is rated <img src="/img/Tv14.gif" width="20" height="20" />
so 13-year-olds with hypersensitive mothers should not proceed
any further!</p>


